_aChangeLog.text: Reverted all textures back to original theme (classic style)
Added new game: Irish Car Bomb (replaced descent)
Added Decals around the map to help tie the theme all in
Added classic colours secret vent from the OG version of jb_troubles
Added secret music room (if abused will be removed)
Changed dodge course song back to the original from OG jb_troubles (cs:go)
People will no longer be unaffected by triggers or teleports (resets targetname on spawn)
Removed Hot Lava option from Skill Jumps {no more MFK day :(}
Made it so surf recall no longer recalls winners
Fixed a misaligned brush in Hide and Seek
Fixed problem with Hide and Seek triggers not removing filter when leaving the game
Fixed a bug in Climb where, if timed correctly, a CT would be teleported with the Ts if caught when another CT changes difficulty
Fixed climb music secret not working
